      "content": "it just seems like a lot of warning for literally one glass of wine... i'm not planning on driving or anything, i'll just be in bed. wouldn't the wine just help the diazepam work faster so i can actually fall asleep? it's not like im drinking a bottle, it's just one drink to help me unwind.",
